{"tid":1215070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 現代雨傘版馬其頓方陣","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:06:34.000Z","uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c23731c596de4602b66e5fe5812b4e73393c9d9e","tid":1215070,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"見到大家都剩係硬食，真係好乖好和平呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8JmLS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8JmLS2.jpg&h=98576dda&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTmrWZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTmrWZF.jpg&h=66034e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人哋打到性起仲露晒成個青頭出嚟<br />\n&quot;覆卓吖，垃圾!&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFMvEcY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFMvEcY.jpg&h=0431e898&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n接住落嚟我係嚟介紹下冷兵器時代嘅一種戰法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/THoqs6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTHoqs6f.jpg&h=bf2ce22d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n正所謂&quot;以子之矛攻子之盾&quot;，矛同盾本身就係天偶佳成嘅組合嚟。點解我咁強調馬其頓? 因為長過30cm囉!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQdNGrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQdNGrg.jpg&h=a669cb68&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n所謂方陣，即係大家齊齊整整唔好散。咁其實近現代嘅火繩槍都係用緊方陣嘅打法嘅，當你一列廿鳩幾人一齊射，就算本身命中率低都可以靠-6<span style=\"color: pink;\">爆頭</span>嘛。<br />\n<br />\n至於盾牌喎，嗱老實就算係精兵要一手揸咁長碌嘢一手揸住舊鐵都咪話唔重，而且仲要兩隻軍長征咁行軍，佢哋揀細盾都好理所當然嘅，咁本身隻盾夠硬囉一定擋到啦。咁但係如果手頭上冇啲咁硬嘅物料，咁咪學下大自然，孔雀開屏又好雞泡魚漲毒好，用個大字嘅area嚟吸引對方嘅準頭靠嚇，誰不知扑落去扑空氣。<br />\n<br />\n哇你話，如果再披埋件咁嘅紅色布做披風，十足十Total War啲古羅馬戰士呀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMjw76h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMjw76h.jpg&h=fde73069&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而馬其頓方陣其實仲有另外一啲特點嘅，就係有側翼同遠程支援啦! 嗱，喺對家俾人督督下嘅期間，冇啦啦有粒嘢飛埋嚟整到成身濕晒污糟晒，退又唔係避又唔係都唔知點好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xk8qs6v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxk8qs6v.gif&h=0b832f03&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHnboEX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHnboEX.gif&h=e5098fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後呢，因為我公司賣遮嘅，想同大家介紹返我哋呢款產品，嗱普通啲遮就分咗傘布斂骨吖，咁穹形嘅骨其實係同塊傘布縫埋一齊嘅，而我呢款八骨嘅，就算你八隻手指都撐得開呀，至於最大嘅賣點，就梗係呢枝可伸可縮嘅手臂延伸啦! 你咪睇佢條條fing咁，靜料嚟㗎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zOfz5To.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzOfz5To.png&h=f9cbb908&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ea17acae0086d4ab90ec74d7f68d9c9c37a25a8","tid":1215070,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:06:34.000Z","msg":"仲遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n看陳雲國師先啦"}]}